, in gcs owned cylinders.</p>\n<p>A full range of CO2 and Mixed gases are available for dispensing drinks. With this service the customer does not have to own cylinders.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>No rental charges</li>\n<li>No deposit</li>\n<li>Food grade quality gases</li>\n<li>Milk-round style regular deliveries</li>\n<li>Food registered premises</li>\n<li>bevgas is a leading local distributor for the hospitality industry in the East Midlands.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To compliment the bevgas service to the hospitality trade, we can also supply Balloon Gas to pubs, clubs or local retail business such as card shops and florists.</p>\n<h2>Contract Filling</h2>\n<p>With our dedicated fleet of ADR-trained drivers and environmentally friendly large goods vehicles, gcs collects, fills and re-delivers customer-owned cylinders in bulk quantity for brewers, wholesalers and independent drinks dispense gas suppliers.</p>\n<p>Pre-fill checks are carried out on all cylinders to ensure they are within test date and in good repair as well as ownership verification.</p>\n<p>If repairs are required or the cylinder is out of test, the cylinder is routed to the cylinder processing plant, rectified/retested, refilled and returned to the customer in full service condition.</p>\n<p>\"Foreign\" cylinders are repatriated to their rightful owners in all cases.</p>\n<h2>Fire Extinguishers</h2>\n<p>We also offer a filling and testing service for large CO2 fire extinguishers.</p>\n',1281539169,1281452769,'',0),('2:23404e8b73f9a2719bceeb69e90a1f94','<div class=\"demo\">\n<div id=\"accordion\">\n<h3><a href=\"#\">Cylinder Testing</a></h3>\n<div>\n<p>\n                                    Mauris mauris ante, blandit et, ultrices a, suscipit eget, quam. Integer ut neque. Vivamus nisi metus, molestie vel, gravida in, condimentum sit amet, nunc. Nam a nibh. Donec suscipit eros. Nam mi. Proin viverra leo ut odio. Curabitur malesuada. Vestibulum a velit eu ante scelerisque vulputate.\n                                </p