h our own refuelling   stations, trailers amd mobile storage packs and are the UK dealers forFuelmaker© compressors.\n                                </p>\n</div>\n<h3><a href=\"#\">BevGAS</a></h3>\n<div>\n<p>\n                                   We have on site facilities to fill cylinders with carbon dioxide, nitrogen and their mixtures used in a variety of applications from drinks dispensing to fire extinguishing.   We provide both a direct delivery of drinks dispense   gases, our bevgas service and contract filling for owners of cylinders.\n                                </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n',1283195948,1283109548,'',0),('2:120b35cd0b66a9dc7dc1f6ad7292b6ac','<p>gcs employs 65 personnel with long term expertise and skills drawn from the cylinder and gases industries and handles in excess of 500,000 units per year through the Nottingham facility.</p>\n<p>Gas Container Services is committed to reducing environmental impact and use natural gas as a fuel for its large goods vehicles and forklift trucks. </p>\n<div class=\"demo\">\n<div id=\"accordion\">\n<h3><a href=\"#\">Cylinder Testing</a></h3>\n<div>\n<p>                 We  carry out periodic inspection and testing of high and low pressure gas cylinders, vessels and drums. <img class=\"photoleft\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/gcs/images/gcs/cylinderscurlsmall.jpg\" /> Our test shop facilities are fully equipped to fully refurbish cylinders, cylinder pack frames and cylinder trailers to as new condition.\n                            </p></div>\n<h3><a href=\"#\">Manufacturing</a></h3>\n<div>\n<p>\n                                    We design and manufacture products for the storage, transportation, control and dispense of high pressure gases for a wide range of industrial and breathing applications.\n                                </p>\n</div>\n<h3><a href=\"#\">Roadgas</a></h3>\n<div>\n<p>\n                                  As RoadGas we  design, manufacture, supply and maintain equipment for the storage,